docs {
  Step 3 of 3: Clinic rehabilitation follow-up workflow.
  Reads the service_capacity relationship for facility fac-4001.
  Uses casework_system persona (rowsKey).
  Together with steps 8-9 this gives: rehabilitation timeline (public works), current
  operational status (facility record), and capacity detail (this relationship).
  Expected: 200 with service capacity records per service_type and month.
}
